@school_token = 
@admin_token = 
### 🔐 Login admin
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123"
}

###

### 🔐 Login school user
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ad1",
  "password": "123"
}

###

### 👤 Lấy thông tin người dùng
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/user/me
Authorization: Bearer {{school_token}}

###

### 🏫 Lấy danh sách trường học
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/school/
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

###

### 📟 Tạo thiết bị mới
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/device/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "name": "ESP32-KhuA",
  "school_id": 1,
  "mac_address": "AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:01"
}

###

### 📟 Danh sách thiết bị
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/device/list
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

###

### 🕰️ Danh sách lịch chuông
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/schedule/
Authorization: Bearer {{school_token}}

###

### ➕ Tạo lịch chuông
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/schedule/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{school_token}}

{
  "day_of_week": 2,
  "start_time": "10:00",
  "end_time": "10:15",
  "bell_type": "Ra chơi",
  "is_summer": false
}

###

### 📝 Sửa lịch chuông
PUT http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/schedule/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{school_token}}

{
  "day_of_week": 1,
  "start_time": "10:20",
  "end_time": "10:35",
  "bell_type": "Điểm tiết",
  "is_summer": false
}

###

### ❌ Xoá lịch chuông
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/schedule/1
Authorization: Bearer {{school_token}}

###

### 📅 Tạo ngày nghỉ
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/holiday/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "name": "Giỗ tổ Hùng Vương",
  "date": "2025-04-18"
}

###

### 📅 Danh sách ngày nghỉ
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/holiday/
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

###

### 📅 Cập nhật ngày nghỉ
PUT http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/holiday/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "name": "Giỗ tổ (updated)",
  "date": "2025-04-19"
}

###

### ❌ Xoá ngày nghỉ
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/holiday/1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

###

### 🌦️ Lấy cấu hình mùa hè
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/season/config
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

###

### 🛠️ Tạo/cập nhật cấu hình mùa hè
PUT http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/season/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "school_id": 1,
  "summer_start": "2025-04-01",
  "summer_end": "2025-09-30"
}

###

### 🕵️‍♂️ Check hôm nay có phải ngày nghỉ không?
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/schedule-helper/is_holiday
Authorization: Bearer {{school_token}}

###

### 📆 Lấy lịch hôm nay
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/schedule-helper/today
Authorization: Bearer {{school_token}}

###

### 📊 Thống kê hệ thống (admin)
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
